{"tid":1947732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［代post］唔知當年係豪景送芒果布甸俾我嘅你而家過成點呢","createTime":"2020-03-28T13:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T13:09:17.000Z","uid":8192,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"37834d76fbabf995b62b538927a45ee0c33b8571","tid":1947732,"uid":8192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"記得好多年前仲係住豪景ge時候<br />\n成日都會落大八方飲茶<br />\n次次都會叫芒果布甸食<br />\n次次都係你拎俾我<br />\n<br />\n久而久之<br />\n我對你就有左果種心動ge感覺<br />\n不過<br />\n果時連你叫咩名都唔知<br />\n唯一知ge係<br />\n只要我一叫芒果布甸就一定會見到你<br />\n<br />\n當我以為呢一切都係必然<br />\n我習慣左你ge存在<br />\n但直到有一日<br />\n當我再叫芒果布甸<br />\n但竟然唔係你拎俾我<br />\n之後先知道<br />\n你已經無做了<br />\n<br />\n#布甸情緣<br />\n#唔知你近年點呢<br />\n#不過好肯定你已經唔記得左我了"},{"pid":"e56b9daf479facc671f0f626d6f71025ff5f45c2","tid":1947732,"uid":8192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"0434f7ff0442228c190b159415817dd150a2b426","tid":1947732,"uid":8192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:08:35.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ebaf4fed9db1bf286b01308e72fc54142a6de46a","tid":1947732,"uid":8192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"34bdcdeb7359b97abb2126d1841e1f1062e67e3f","tid":1947732,"uid":8192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"af77cbfc1d4083b9e732317132a8a8e00a74fc72","tid":1947732,"uid":8192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:09:17.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}